data.name: TagCommand
data.value: Adds files to the current session index based on the provided filter.

data.name: PrintCommand
data.value: Print files that are currently tagged (in the index).

data.name: RecursiveOp
data.value: Recurse depth to tag up until. 0 (default) denotes no recursion, values less than 0 denote no limit.

data.name: HelpCommand
data.value: Extended information on various commands and topics in FsTag.

data.name: RmLabelAllCommand
data.value: Remove all labels from indexed files.

data.name: RmLabelCommand
data.value: Remove the specified label from index files.

data.name: LabelCommand
data.value: Set the specified label on indexed files.

data.name: LabelNewOp
data.value: Only set labels where they aren't already set.

data.name: DeleteRecycle
data.value: Whether to send deleted items to the recycle bin.
